'''彼得·納瓦羅'''（{{lang|en|Peter Navarro}}，{{bd|1949年|7月15日||}}）是一名美国经济学家，前任[[美国总统|美國總統]]助理<ref>{{Cite web|title=White House introduces Dr. Peter Navarro|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/people/peter-navarro/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120140938/https://www.whitehouse.gov/people/peter-navarro/}}</ref>、白宮貿易與製造業政策辦公室主任<ref name="appoint">{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/greatagain/navarro-national-trade-council-c2d90c10eacb|title=President-Elect Donald J. Trump Appoints Dr. Peter Navarro to Head the White House National Trade Council|first=The Transition|last=Team|date=December 21, 2016|website=Medium|access-date=2020-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408144445/https://medium.com/greatagain/navarro-national-trade-council-c2d90c10eacb|archive-date=2019-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[國防生產法|《國防生產法》]]政策協調員<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/mar/27/trump-taps-peter-navarro-to-run-national-defense-p/|title=Trump taps Peter Navarro to run national defense production for emergency medical supplies|author=|date=Mar 27, 2020|work=The Washington Times|publisher=华盛顿时报|accessdate=Mar 27, 2020|language=en|format=|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704044335/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/mar/27/trump-taps-peter-navarro-to-run-national-defense-p/}}</ref>。他是[[加利福尼亞大學爾灣分校|加利福尼亚大学尔湾分校]]保罗梅拉吉商学院经济学和公共政策退休教授。他出版了数十部书籍，包括《[[致命中国|致命中国]]》。他也在同行评议学术杂志上发表了多篇关于能源政策、慈善机构、垃圾的回收和经济因素的经济学研究论文。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.economist.com/briefing/2017/01/21/peter-navarro-is-about-to-become-one-of-the-worlds-most-powerful-economists|title=Peter Navarro is about to become one of the world’s most powerful economists|website=The Economist|accessdate=June 10, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150909/https://www.economist.com/briefing/2017/01/21/peter-navarro-is-about-to-become-one-of-the-worlds-most-powerful-economists|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

納瓦羅的观点处于主流经济学之外，被普遍看成非主流经济学家。<ref>Justin Wolfers, [https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/11/upshot/why-most-economists-are-so-worried-about-trump.html Why Most Economists Are So Worried About Trump] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/11/upshot/why-most-economists-are-so-worried-about-trump.html |date=20180612182124 }}, ''New York Times'' (January 11, 2017): "stands so far outside the mainstream that he endorses few of the key tenets of the profession."</ref><ref>[https://www.economist.com/blogs/democracyinamerica/2017/02/trump-s-cabinet The wonkless White House] {{Wayback|url=https://www.economist.com/blogs/democracyinamerica/2017/02/trump-s-cabinet |date=20171021010625 }}, ''Economist'' (February 2017): "Mr Navarro’s views on trade are well outside the mainstream, and he is not a big hitter in academic circles."</ref><ref name="Coy">Peter Coy, [https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-03-08/after-defeating-cohn-trump-s-trade-warrior-is-on-the-rise-again After Defeating Cohn, Trump's Trade Warrior Is on the Rise Again] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-03-08/after-defeating-cohn-trump-s-trade-warrior-is-on-the-rise-again |date=20190327144458 }}, Bloomberg (March 8, 2018): "Navarro has come a long way from his roots as a mainstream economist."</ref>他强烈要求降低美国贸易逆差，经常批评德国和中国进行货币操控。他要求扩大美国制造业规模、建立高关税、全球供应链回流。他强烈反对[[北美自由贸易协议|北美自由贸易协定]]和[[跨太平洋伙伴关系协定|跨太平洋伙伴关系协定]]。他与美国商务部长[[威尔伯·罗斯|威尔伯·罗斯]]共同为[[唐納德·川普|川普]]的竞选和任职期间，创立了基础设施开发计划。<ref name="Mufson">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/economists-pan-infrastructure-plan-championed-by-trump-nominees/2017/01/17/0ed1ad5e-dc5e-11e6-918c-99ede3c8cafa_story.html|title=Economists pan infrastructure plan championed by Trump nominees|first=Steven|last=Mufson|date=January 17, 2017|publisher=|accessdate=June 10, 2018|via=www.washingtonpost.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803150319/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/economists-pan-infrastructure-plan-championed-by-trump-nominees/2017/01/17/0ed1ad5e-dc5e-11e6-918c-99ede3c8cafa_story.html|archive-date=2018-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="peternavarro.com">{{Cite web |url=http://peternavarro.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/infrastructurereport.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729093231/http://peternavarro.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/infrastructurereport.pdf |archive-date=2018-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 早年生平 ==
納瓦羅於1949年7月15日出生在美國[[麻薩諸塞州|馬薩諸塞州]]的劍橋市。父親Alfred Navarro是一名薩克斯手和單簧管演奏家，母親Evelyn Littlejohn在一家百貨公司擔任秘書。在他9歲時，父母離異，他與哥哥跟隨母親先後在佛羅裡達州棕櫚灘、馬裡蘭州貝塞斯達生活長大。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Navarro Says Loan for Race Was Inherited : Politics: Mayoral candidate admits $300,000 was given to him by his mother, but all the money has been spent.|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1992-08-08-me-4514-story.html|accessdate=2020-07-06|date=1992-08-08|last=Facebook|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309025707/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1992-08-08-me-4514-story.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=10 Things You Didn't Know About Peter Navarro|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/national-news/articles/2017-03-10/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-peter-navarro|accessdate=|author=|date=March 10, 2017|format=|publisher=USNEWS|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706163538/https://www.usnews.com/news/national-news/articles/2017-03-10/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-peter-navarro}}</ref>

== 教育背景 ==
納瓦羅在[[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大學]]取得學士和碩士學位，並在[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]取得博士學位<ref name="PMSB" />。在開始教學工作前，曾任[[和平工作團|和平工作團]]的成員和在[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]擔任能源和公共政策顧問<ref name="PMSB-Awards" />。後來擔任[[爾灣加利福尼亞大學|爾灣加利福尼亞大學]]保羅·梅拉吉商學院的教授<ref name="TG" />。

== 政治生涯 ==
納瓦羅曾經是一名[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]人，曾三次爭取進入[[加州|加州]][[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|圣地亚哥]]市政厅。1992年，竞选市长败于共和党人{{le|苏珊·戈尔丁|Susan Golding}}<ref name="CSD-M" />。1996年，代表民主党竞选第49国会选区议员席位，再次败给了共和党人{{le|布赖恩·比尔布雷|Brian Bilbray}}<ref name="BP-CA49" />。2001年，纳瓦罗竞选圣地亚哥市政厅第六席位的特别选举，又在初选中失败<ref name="CSD-CD6" />。

2016年，纳瓦罗担任[[唐納德·特朗普|唐納德·川普]]选举团队的政策顾问<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vox.com/2016/8/5/12387698/trump-billionaires-economists |title=Trump's economic team has a lot of billionaires, very few economic experts |last1=Lee |first1=Timothy B. |last2= |first2= |date=August 5, 2016 |website=Vox |publisher= |access-date=August 7, 2016 |quote=...the list includes only one academic economist. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126203813/http://www.vox.com/2016/8/5/12387698/trump-billionaires-economists |archive-date=2017-01-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年12月21日，他被候任總統唐納德·川普提名為整合現有[[美國國家安全會議|美國國家安全會議]]（NSC）、國家經濟會議（NEC）及國內政策會議（Domestic Policy Council）而新設立的[[白宮國家貿易委員會|白宮國家貿易委員會]]（National Trade Council）主任<ref name=TG />。

2017年4月，白宮國家貿易委員會轉型為白宮貿易與製造業政策辦公室（White House Office of Trade and Manufacturing Policy; OTMP），仍由納瓦羅擔任主任<ref>{{cite web |title=Trump orders the establishment of an Office of Trade and Manufacturing Policy, to be run by Navarro |url=https://insidetrade.com/daily-news/trump-orders-establishment-office-trade-and-manufacturing-policy-be-run-navarro |website=World Trade Online (2017-04-29) |accessdate=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701194419/https://insidetrade.com/daily-news/trump-orders-establishment-office-trade-and-manufacturing-policy-be-run-navarro |archive-date=2018-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年6月28日，納瓦羅在華盛頓智庫哈德遜研究所（Hudson Institute）發表演講，主要是介紹OTMP辦公室發布的一份有關中國對美國經濟與國家安全造成損害的六大策略及50多種行為、政策與作法的圖表。<ref>{{cite web |title=納瓦羅罕見公開亮相細數中國“經濟侵略”招數 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/navarro-chinese-economy-20180629/4460675.html |website=VOA (2018-06-29) |accessdate=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702011011/https://www.voachinese.com/a/navarro-chinese-economy-20180629/4460675.html |archive-date=2018-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=How China’s Economic Aggression Threatens the Technologies and Intellectual Property of the United States and the World |date=2018-06-19 |publisher=White House Office of Trade and Manufacturing Policy |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/FINAL-China-Technology-Report-6.18.18-PDF.pdf |accessdate=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628055548/https://www.whitehouse.gov/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/FINAL-China-Technology-Report-6.18.18-PDF.pdf |archive-date=2018-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Office of Trade & Manufacturing Policy Report: “How China’s Economic Aggression Threatens the Technologies and Intellectual Property of the United States and the World” |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/office-trade-manufacturing-policy-report-chinas-economic-aggression-threatens-technologies-intellectual-property-united-states-world/ |website=Whitehouse (2018-06-19) |accessdate=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701194057/https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/office-trade-manufacturing-policy-report-chinas-economic-aggression-threatens-technologies-intellectual-property-united-states-world/ |archive-date=2018-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年1月21日，中華人民共和國外交部宣布對28名美國人及其親屬實施制裁，納瓦羅是其中1人。

== 政治派別 ==
納瓦羅的政治派別和政策立場被《經濟學人》週刊描述為「爭議激烈，跨度很大」。<ref name="#1">{{Cite journal|title=Peter Navarro is about to become one of the world’s most powerful economists|url=https://www.economist.com/briefing/2017/01/21/peter-navarro-is-about-to-become-one-of-the-worlds-most-powerful-economists|journal=The Economist|issn=0013-0613|access-date=2018-06-21|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150909/https://www.economist.com/briefing/2017/01/21/peter-navarro-is-about-to-become-one-of-the-worlds-most-powerful-economists|dead-url=no}}</ref>他早期曾註冊過民主黨人，獨立黨人甚至無黨派人士。在加入川普政府後一段時間，還曾被認為是民主黨人，2018年2月，納瓦羅重新登記為共和黨人。<ref>{{Cite news|title=In the Battles Over Trump’s Trade Wars, Hawkish Adviser Navarro Endures|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/in-the-battles-over-trumps-trade-wars-hawkish-adviser-navarro-endures-11576943074|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2019-12-21|accessdate=2020-07-06|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Alex|last=Leary|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217214410/https://www.wsj.com/articles/in-the-battles-over-trumps-trade-wars-hawkish-adviser-navarro-endures-11576943074|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 理論觀點 ==

=== 特殊利益集團對美國工人利益的損害 ===
納瓦羅的經濟觀點具有平民主義的視角，他在1984年出版的《政策遊戲：特殊利益集團和思想家如何竊取美國》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Peter Navarro's radical transformation|url=https://www.axios.com/peter-navarro-free-trade-globalist-the-policy-game-book-7e2739be-104b-41cf-a5b6-986ac66f213a.html|accessdate=2020-07-10|last=Swan|first=Erica Pandey,Jonathan|work=Axios|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906043103/https://www.axios.com/peter-navarro-free-trade-globalist-the-policy-game-book-7e2739be-104b-41cf-a5b6-986ac66f213a.html}}</ref>一書中論述了特殊利益集團將美國引向了「其歷史上無法增長和繁榮的地步」。在書中，他還呼籲加大對工人的補償，以幫助那些因貿易和外國競爭而失去工作的人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Peter Navarro's radical transformation|url=https://www.axios.com/peter-navarro-free-trade-globalist-the-policy-game-book-7e2739be-104b-41cf-a5b6-986ac66f213a.html|accessdate=2020-07-06|last=Swan|first=Erica Pandey,Jonathan|work=Axios|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906043103/https://www.axios.com/peter-navarro-free-trade-globalist-the-policy-game-book-7e2739be-104b-41cf-a5b6-986ac66f213a.html}}</ref>

=== 保護美國利益反對多邊自由貿易協定 ===
納瓦羅旗幟鮮明地反對[[跨太平洋夥伴全面進展協定|跨太平洋夥伴關係]]（TPP），他在2015年4月的一篇專欄文章中說：「為了吸引我們，他們的代言人吹噓TPP將刺激美國出口，以刺激急需的經濟增長。事實上，美國經濟將嚴重受損。這是因為TPP將打擊經濟增長的兩大驅動力——國內投資和淨出口。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Parsing the Trans-Pacific Partnership agreement|url=https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/238473-parsing-the-trans-pacific-partnership-agreement|accessdate=2020-07-06|date=2015-04-13|last=Picard|first=Joe|work=TheHill|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421104527/https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/238473-parsing-the-trans-pacific-partnership-agreement}}</ref>納瓦羅也反對[[北美自由贸易协议|北美自由貿易協定]]（NAFTA），認為應啟動雙邊貿易談判，達成更有利於美國的協議。

=== 中美不公平貿易問題和來自中國的威脅 ===
納瓦羅曾撰寫了多部與中國有關的書籍，形成了一套有別於主流經濟學派的中美關係理論。在2006年出版的《即將到來的中國戰爭》<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Coming China Wars|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=The_Coming_China_Wars&oldid=884896192|date=2019-02-24|journal=Wikipedia|language=en}}</ref>一書中，納瓦羅研究了中國作為一個新興的世界大國，在國際商業中的作用如何與世界各國在能源、自然資源、環境、知識產權和其他問題上產生衝突。在2008年出版的《行走的赤龍：新興的中國經濟及其對世界的影響》一書中，納瓦羅分析了中國作為世界工廠向全世界提供廉價商品可能對地球的健康和安全產生的可怕後果，並提到價格競爭、產業鏈轉移、環境污染的等問題以及可能對美國政治獨立和金融市場產生的重大影響。2011年出版的《致命中國》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chết Dưới Tay Trung Quốc: Đối Đầu Với... book by Peter Navarro|url=https://www.thriftbooks.com/w/death-by-china-confronting-the-dragon---a-global-call-to-action_peter-navarro_greg-autry/3138267/|accessdate=2020-07-07|last=ThriftBooks|work=ThriftBooks|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013003341/https://www.thriftbooks.com/w/death-by-china-confronting-the-dragon---a-global-call-to-action_peter-navarro_greg-autry/3138267/}}</ref>是納瓦羅最有影響力的一本書，他在書中指責中國政府通過操控貨幣和大幅補貼，向美國市場傾銷質量低劣、價格便宜的商品，從而衝垮了美國的製造業和中產階級，直接造成了美國的空心化和一系列社會問題。並批評中國強迫美國公司交出知識產權作為進入中國市場的條件，憑藉「更自由地污染環境，遠低於美國的雇傭工人條件」獲得低成本優勢，違反了公平貿易原則，使美國公司「幾乎不可能」參與競爭，因為他們不是在與中國公司競爭，而是在與中國政府競爭"<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Death by China,’ Documentary Directed by Peter Navarro - The New York Times|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118000232/https:/www.nytimes.com/2012/08/24/movies/death-by-china-documentary-directed-by-peter-navarro.html|accessdate=2020-07-07|date=2017-11-18|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>。除了經濟影響力，納瓦羅還在2015年出版的《臥虎：中國軍國主義對世界意味著什麼》一書中談到中國的意識形態和軍事威脅。認為世界需要共同努力，防止他們欺負鄰國，阻止類似“[[孔子学院|孔子學院]]”這樣的組織影響和傳播宣傳。

== 爭議人物 ==
納瓦羅的觀點在彼時全球化背景下，顯得特立獨行, 既使其獲得眾多支持者，也遭到了主流媒體、經濟學家的批評。

=== 支持方 ===
